precis:
Enactment of the SOFTWOOD LUMBER PRODUCTS EXPORT PERMITS FEES REGULATIONS
which set out the fees to be paid for the issuance of a permit to export
softwood lumber products to the U.S. where they were first manufactured in
the Provinces of Alberta, British Columbia, Ontario or Quebec.
